  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: Intradialytic blood pressure and dialysis efficacy (in terms of urea removal)
      improve under electrical muscle stimulation or passive leg movement on a treadmill.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
